{"lastModified":1752145470031,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nDREAM is a 16.56m / 54ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2025 by Lagoon. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 3. Cruising at 8.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 10.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise of four double cabins and one twin cabin (convertible to double), all with en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"DREAM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48d0cac0-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48bef070-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48c3ab60-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48e4ef00-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48a8f770-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48e5d960-1aae-11f0-99da-f98d3eda3eaa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48e82350-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48e64e90-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48d118e0-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48e6c3c0-1aae-11f0-960c-139f4e55d84b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::48e60070-1aae-11f0-8133-ff35b5648fd0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image: