in my life, shaping both my personal and professional journey. From a young age, I developed a deep love for sailing, a passion that led me to achieve success at the highest levels, both as an athlete and as a trainer. Driven by my connection to the water, I sought to merge my enthusiasm for sailing with tourism, creating unique experiences for those wishing to explore the beauty of the sea. Over the past 15 years, I have dedicated myself to the management and maintenance of both private and professional boats. This work has allowed me to combine technical expertise with a deep understanding of nautical operations. Acting as Captain, I have been responsible for vessels up to 70 feet in length. These experiences have allowed me to refine essential skills such as leadership, teamwork, and meticulous attention to detail. My strong sense of order and team-oriented mindset ensure that guests will experience smooth and enjoyable voyages. The sea continues to be my inspiration, guiding me to deliver excellence and memorable experiences for everyone who shares my love for life on the water."},{"name":"Sotiris Solomos","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819307041::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::bd1cb050-3a3f-11f0-865d-ef4a20ee5f8e/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Sotiris, has began his professional career providing service as bartender and high standards service in high-end restaurants in Santorini and Monaco.\nHe has been a chef onboard catamarans and motor yachts since 2016. Sotiris provided high standard of service and managed the wine menu for private yachts. His culinary skills along with passion for travelling led him join the yachting industry. He is a hard working person with excellent customer service skills and takes pride in providing the best service to those onboard. His ability to create delightful menus according to individual preferences made him stand out to those who cruised with him. He speaks Greek (native), English (fluent)."},{"name":"Vaggelis Psallidas","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7819307041::vessel::b6f45100-1aab-11f0-9f47-571c21c8aa15::assets::01646500-3a40-11f0-9f25-c7996571325a/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Vaggelis Psallidas is a 25-year-old deckhand with a deep passion for sailing and life at sea. With a natural affinity for the ocean, he finds both freedom and balance in his time on the water. His athletic background enhances his performance onboard, allowing him to bring focus, discipline, and energy to every charter. Vaggelis is dedicated, hardworking, and eager to contribute to memorable and safe experiences for all guests."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2200000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2200000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3100000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3100000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"High Season (July - August)","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":3100000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":3100000,"amount":3100000,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.13}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.25,"unitPrice":3100000,"amount":775000}],"total":4278000,"subTotal":3875000,"totalTax":403000},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Greece","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Greece"],"coordinates":[24.261736188816826,38.42232351533858],"bbox":[19.646484375,34.934472656249994,28.231835937500023,41.743798828124994]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"Mid-Season (June - September)","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2